{"text_id":13569,"tokens":["This"," paper"," presents"," a"," comprehensive"," study"," of"," the"," catastrophic"," eruption"," of"," a"," magnetic"," flux"," rope"," (","M","FR",")"," in"," the"," corona"," and"," solar"," wind",","," both"," with"," and"," without"," magnetic"," re","connection","."," We"," employ"," a"," three","-","dimensional"," magneto","hydro","dynamic"," (","M","HD",")"," simulation"," to"," model"," the"," dynamics"," of"," the"," M","FR"," and"," its"," interaction"," with"," the"," surrounding"," plasma"," environment","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," the"," M","FR"," eruption"," is"," a"," complex"," process"," involving"," a"," delicate"," interplay"," between"," magnetic"," forces",","," plasma"," pressure",","," and"," gravitational"," forces","."," We"," find"," that"," magnetic"," re","connection"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," the"," onset"," and"," evolution"," of"," the"," eruption",","," leading"," to"," a"," significant"," acceleration"," of"," the"," M","FR"," and"," a"," drastic"," change"," in"," the"," topology"," of"," the"," magnetic"," field","."," In"," the"," absence"," of"," re","connection",","," the"," eruption"," is"," slower"," and"," less"," violent",","," but"," still"," leads"," to"," a"," substantial"," perturbation"," in"," the"," corona"," and"," solar"," wind","."," These"," findings"," provide"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," physics"," of"," solar"," eruptions"," and"," have"," important"," implications"," for"," space"," weather"," forecasting","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}